    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows; the paint is flawless and the interior is still crisp and spotless. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and well-kept, this is the one. Come grab the keys and see for yourself! \u2728",
