    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1) in pristine condition. This example features the naturally aspirated 3.8L boxer engine, delivering 355 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and remains factory-spec, exhibiting exceptional torsional rigidity and telepathic steering feedback. Significant preventative maintenance includes a retrofitted IMS bearing and a documented cooling system refresh. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with zero imperfections, while the interior leather shows no bolster wear. Mechanically flawless with a clean DME over-rev report, this is a turn-key performance machine for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
